keywords cleric clerics
---
Clerics are divine casters who treat faith as institutional infrastructure rather than personal devotion.
They descend from the Solar Court of the Undivided Disk, specifically the Dawn Liturgists and Seal College.
The Shard Doctrine defines the class: the Black Sun Shard is an active metaphysical threat requiring continuous ritual maintenance.
Rites are maintenance procedures that keep cosmic machinery functioning, not expressions of worship.
Combat role is support caster with offensive divine magic, protective wards, and healing capability.
Under the Violet Compact's registry law, clerics hold formal civic standing in the crossroads cities.
The tradition has public outer and secret inner layers preserving Solar Court technical knowledge.
Clerics oppose Necromancers, holding that unauthorized spirit-sustaining destabilizes cosmic containment.
The Paladin and Priest traditions both split from the cleric lineage after the Sundering Wars.
